368
00:22:47,990 --> 00:22:51,139
♪Returning to the land
Left bare by the receding sea♪

369
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:53,909
♪Withering like a fallen leaf♪

370
00:22:53,910 --> 00:22:57,559
♪The message in a bottle
buried on the shore♪

371
00:22:57,560 --> 00:23:00,710
♪No one asked♪

372
