♪Together forever in my dreams♪

380
00:23:34,170 --> 00:23:40,480
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

381
00:23:40,490 --> 00:23:44,299
♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

382
00:23:44,300 --> 00:23:47,149
♪And swim with me to you♪

383
00:23:47,150 --> 00:23:50,839
♪I'd become♪

384
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:53,839
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

385
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:57,559
♪If love is like a night storm♪

386
00:23:57,560 --> 00:24:00,799
♪Unable to stop for a moment♪

387
